Scripts


randomwallpaper [OPTIONS]

 Options:
   -t <time>                Set global wait time (default:1m)
   -d <DIR>                 Set wallpaper directory (default:$XDG_PICTURES_DIR/Wallpapers)
   -c <config file>         Use config file to set wait time for individual images
   -w <wallpaper handler>   Set wallpaper handler manually (default:auto)
   -l                       List all wallpaper handlers
   -h or -?                 Show help (this message)

Config file format:
<part of filename> <wait time for this image>
[another filename] <wait time for this image>
and so on.


loop-command <sleep time> <command> [command args...]

Options:
-h or -?                 Show help (this message)


rmaudio [OPTIONS]

Options:
 -d                       Remove input file after conversion
 -h or -?                 Show help (this message)
"

run-one-instance-only [COMMAND]
wrapper to run COMMAND only when "killall -e -0" returned false, ie. when COMMAND is not running.
